name: Pure
description: Pure reflects my inner journey; specifically, the experiences that made me into a survivor, artist, and poet. The victory that the poem and art piece reflect is a rebirth of softness. The figure’s eyes are wide, as are mine, open to the odyssey of new encounters that each new day presents. "Pure" is featured in BIT.SHES Gallery Collection iDENTITY | 01 | Vol. 2 — All proceeds from this piece go to charity. Check out bitshes.com for more info!
